%% Diagram: Diagram 3
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart LR
    subgraph Tiers["Index Tiers"]
        HOT[(Hot Tier<br/>Memory/SSD<br/>Top 10% pages)]
        WARM[(Warm Tier<br/>SSD<br/>Next 30% pages)]
        COLD[(Cold Tier<br/>HDD<br/>Remaining 60%)]
    end

    Query --> HOT
    HOT -->|Miss| WARM
    WARM -->|Miss| COLD
